===========  EX DESCRIPTION =============================================
This code apply the game "Connect4". It consists of 7 classes out of which 2 related to GUI:
1. Game - responsible for the main moves in the game and for the connection with the board
2. Board - manages the state of the board at any given time
3. GameRunner - ?
4. Disc - creates the Disc object
5. Ai - this class manage automatic game moves that will be operated by computer-set_player
6. Start window - a GUI class that created the opening window and deal with set_player selection
7. Gui - the main GUI class

the file four_in_a_row.py creates the main objects of the game and thus run it








